Namun nelayan tersebut tidak pernah pulang lagi ke pangkuan isteri dan anaknya.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan konflik yang berlaku dalam diri Hafizi yang membawa diri ke sebuah kampung tempat lokasi di mana berlakunya kejadian kapal terbang terhempas di Tanjung Kupang. Kehadirannya di kampung itu disambut baik pemilik homestay tempatnya menginap, Haji Isa yang terkenal dengan keramahan dan tinggi ilmu agama. Situasi itu membuatkan Hafizi selesa dalam meneruskan misi menunaikan wasiat ibunya.

programme.title: Drama Tamil – Brindavanam Ep13/EpAkhir
programme.desc: Rajan merupakan seorang pelukis potret yang tinggal di sebuah pusat jagaan orang tua bernama Brindavanam. Rajan merupakan seorang yang aktif dan terkenal dalam bidang seni lukis dan khususnya lukisan potret. Rajan mempunyai sebuah keluarga yang bahagia terdiri daripada isterinya Kalyani, anak lelakinya Rakesh, menantunya Dania dan dua orang cucu. Rajan amat menyayangi keluargannya namun ianya sama penting dengan kerjayanya sebagai pelukis.

programme.title: Bicara Cinta Tertangguh Ep12
programme.desc: Nani terperanjat apabila Damia memberitahu yang dia menyukai Luqman. Suriya merasa cemburu apabila melihat Luqman melayan Damia. Luqman mengakui dia menyukai Damia, tetapi dia menyintai Suriya. Setelah tahu siapa Luqman yang sebenarnya, Nani dan Damia membuat perancangan untuk merampas Luqman dari Suriya.

programme.title: Mek Gyver 2 Ep5
programme.desc: Razif terangkan perancangannya. Zarra memiliki wang satu juta dalam akaunnya. Amy terkejut. Razif berjanji akan mengahwini Amy dan menceraikan Zarra selepas mendapat duit itu. Amy ikut saja asalkan Razif berpegang pada kata-katanya.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep13
programme.desc: Rahman masih terkejut, dia memberitahu bahawa Adi adalah anaknya dengan bukti dokumen yang ditunjukkan oleh Adi itu. Lalu Rahman membawa Adi berjumpa dengan Zainab (mak kandung Adi). Mereka menyuruh Adi tinggal bersama dengan mereka, tetapi Adi memilih untuk tinggal di madrasah sahaja. Sekali sekala Zainab menyuruh Sakinah menjemput Adi untuk datang ke rumah mereka, Rahman dan Zainab mahu memberikan apa sahaja untuk Adi kerana dia telah meninggalkan Adi hampir 20 tahun. Zainab dan Rahman mahu jodohkan Adi dengan Sakinah.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep27

Ezgi dan zgr juga berpura-pura tidak sesuai antara satu sama lain agar tidak menyusahkan keluarga mereka. Ini membuatkan keluarga mereka sangsi dengan perkahwinan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Gila Gusti
programme.desc: Mamat dan Zul taksub dengan ahli gusti bernama Naga. Apabila Naga kalah dalam perlawanan, mereka memberinya kasih sayang persaudaraan untuk berjaya semula.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep05
programme.desc: Lukman masih dihantui mimpi dan kenangan bersama arwah Sarah. Perasaan bersalah atas kematian Sarah tetap mengganggu minda dan emosinya. Dia sering terbayangkan arwah Sarah ketika bersama Farah. Perasaan kelirunya membuatkan Farah sering makan hati. Farah cuba menggoda Lukman, namun Lukman menolak dirinya hingga Farah jadi tawar hati. Lantaran kecewa dengan penolakan Lukman, Farah merajuk dan meminta Liza menghantarnya pulang ke rumah mak abah di kampung. Myra pula tiba- tiba kembali ke pejabat, minta maaf dengan semua orang dan memohon agar dirinya diterima bekerja semula. Liza terkejut apabila Farah sanggup berlari keluar dari kereta dan berlari ke jambatan seolah-olah mahu bunuh diri. Lukman sakit hati apabila Zulkarnain menyindir kononnya dia tak tahu menjaga isteri. Di kampung, Farah bertemu dengan Nazim dan mereka mengimbau kenangan lama semula.

programme.title: Aroma Masak S3 Ep18
programme.desc: Tak tahu nak masak apa hari ni? Bosan makan diluar? Jom memasak bersama selebriti kesayangan anda dalam Aroma Masak yang dihoskan oleh Syafie Naswip dan tetamu jemputannya, Atu Zero.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep18
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep13
programme.desc: Farah tidak mampu lagi memaafkan Lukman apabila sekali lagi bertembung dengan Myra di dalam rumah Lukman. Seluruh kepercayaan sudah lerai. Dia keluar dari rumah dan enggan berjumpa dengan Lukman lagi. Dia sanggup tinggal di hotel demi menjauhkan diri daripada semua orang. Lukman resah apabila tidak dapat mencari Farah namun hal itu disembunyikan daripada familinya. Segalanya berpunca daripada Myra yang datang ke rumah demi mengadukan konon dirinya teraniaya. Pihak pengurusan syarikat mendapat bukti bahawa Lukman terbabit dalam kehilangan wang syarikat. Abah tidak percaya dengan tindakan Farah yang nekad ke UK meninggalkan suami dan Zahin. Budi mengesyaki ada yang tak kena dengan kes Lukman. Farah pula menanggalkan cincin perkahwinan lalu diserahkan kepada Lukman. Dia sudah redha apa sahaja jalinan takdirnya. Lukman ditahan polis untuk siasatan kes pecah amanah.

programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep07
programme.desc: Memaparkan Mizan keluar rumah meninggalkan Sheila dan ibu bapanya. Hani ketika berada di rumah Yusri/Sarah dihubungi ibu mentuanya meminta dia pulang. Sebelum itu, Khalid berharap Mizan membantunya untuk mendekati wanita idamannya. Mengikut Khalid wanita itu begitu sempurna sukar ditemui. Hani bergegas pulang dan di hadapan rumah dia ternampak dan dengar Suria sedang merayu dan memujuk Mizan, sedangkan Mizan marah serta meminta dia beredar. Di situlah Hani diperkenalkan Mizan sebagai isterinya, lantas Suria beredar. Hani meminta kebenaran Mizan untuk pulang ke kampung dan tidak disetujui Mizan keranai bimbang adiknya Nizam begitu mencintai Hani. Mizan salah faham permintaan ibunya agar Hani pulang untuk membantu Sheila. Mizan juga tidak tahu Nizam telah keluar rumah. Mizan sebenarnya salah sangka akhirnya membenarkan Hani dan dia juga semakin menyayangi Hani, tetapi memendamkannya. Semasa Hani menjaga Sheila di wad, Sheila mencerca Hani sebagai cuba merampas suaminya, cuba menunjuk baik kepada mentua dan berbagai-bagai. Sheila tidak menyukai Hani membantunya. Susulan itu, Hani tenang dan sabar kerana dia diamanah ibu dan bapa mentuanya. Hani juga menghubungi Nizam merayu pulang mendampingi Sheila, Nizam sebenarnya ke Langkawi dan bertegas tidak menyukai Sheila dan tidak akan pulang, malahan sanggup berbual semata-mata kerana Hani.

programme.title: Bib S1 Ep23
programme.desc: Hud (Razali Hussien) merupakan seorang wartawan telah membuat laporan penyiasatan ekslusif tentang kejadian tanah runtuh di sebuah taman tema. Ia berpunca daripada pembangunan yang tidak menepati piawaian alam sekitar sehingga taman tema itu diarahkan tutup. Tiara (Faradhiya) pula seorang aktivis alam sekitar begitu tertarik kepada Hud kerana keberaniannya menentang penjenayah alam sekitar. Namun, Tiara yang baru pulang dari luar negara, tidak menyedari yang penjenayah itu adalah bapanya sendiri, Tan Sri Selamat Rahmat.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep08
programme.desc: Farah panik apabila Zahin demam panas hingga muntah-muntah. Keadaan Zahin menyebabkan Farah dan Lukman dalam dilema untuk menyerahkan tugas menjaga Zahin kerana masing-masing sedang sibuk. Farah mengalah dan terpaksa ambil cuti kecemasan meskipun dia baru bekerja. Kata-kata pedih daripada pengurusnya, Dahlia membuatkan Farah makin burn-out. Farah menemukan diari arwah Farah yang meluahkan segala yang terpendam ketika hayatnya. Kak Yati yang baru pulang dari luar negara datang bersama Mama untuk menziarahi Zahin. Mama bising-bising kerana Farah tidak memberitahunya akan keadaan Zahin. Pertama kali bertemu, Farah rasa sangat selesa dengan Kak Yati. Myra terus mendesak Lukman meminjamkannya RM50,000 untuk adiknya yang bakal membuka bisnes katering. Dia tidak berpuas hati kerana Lukman memberikan tidak sampai separuh yang diminta. Joshua pula menggunakan wang tersebut untuk membayar

programme.title: Lakaran Cinta
programme.desc: Maliqa, gadis buta yang mempunyai sahabat baik bernama wafi yang menjadi pencerita untuk maliqa melakar lukisannya. Wafi sudah berpindah ke kuala lumpur, suatu hari wafi pulang dengan membawa khabar dia mahu berkahwin tetapi niatnya tergendala. Segalanya dirahsiakan demi menjaga hubungan persahabatan itu. Suatu hari, ibu maliqa jatuh tergelincir dan meninggal dunia. Saat itu, melihat maliqa yang sering bersedih, puan maya memberitahu wafi tentang impian rosnah dan puan maya. Tanpa merekas sangka, wafi terus mengambil keputusan untuk berkahwin dengan maliqa tanpa dipaksa.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep28
programme.desc: Ezgi sangat terharu dengan kejutan zgr. Semua kebencian terhadap zgr berlalu. Dalam proses ini, kedua-duanya lebih memahami betapa mereka menghargai satu sama lain. Mereka membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka, tidak ada lagi tempat untuk pembohongan. Jadi mereka memutuskan untuk memberitahu keluarga mereka bahawa mereka bersama. Nevin menerima perhubungan ini walaupun dia tidak menginginkannya sangat, Sevim pula tidak mahu Ezgi dan zgr bersama. Ezgi mengadakan acara pertamanya di syarikat organisasi yang diupahnya, dan kejutan menantinya di acara ini. programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani menemani Sheila yang sakit hendak bersalin. Sheila memarahi dan meminta Hani tidak perlu menemainya. Dia keletihan dan ibunya meminta dia berehat dan tidur awal. Mizan pula mengutamakan ke kampungnya daripada majlis jemputan tetapi tiba lewat malam, Hani telah nyenyak tidur. programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lekaki yang membela hantu raya yang di warisi oleh ayahnya dengan terpaksa. Namun lama kelamaan dia mula suka dengan saka belaan tersebut. Setelah bertahun-tahun dan usianya yang menghampiri kematian, pak Harun mula sedar dan cuba membuang hantu raya tersebut yang mula menganggu penduduk kampung. Apatah lagi anak gadisnya putus tunang akibat dia membela hantu raya tersebut. Pak Harun akhirnya berjaya membuang hantu raya tersebut dengan bantuan seorang ustaz. Pak harun akhirnya meninggal dunia, anak dan isterinya berpindah selepas kematian pak harun

programme.title: The Hoarder
programme.desc: Ella dipaksa bekerja dengan sekumpulan orang asing yang menakutkan selepas terperangkap di kemudahan penyimpanan bawah tanah di mana dia mendapati dirinya diburu oleh pembunuh yang tidak dikenali.

programme.title: Ropes
programme.desc: Ann bersama keluarganya, suami dan anak perempuannya serta ibunya berpindah ke tempat baru dimana mereka berharap untuk hidup lebih baik. Bagaimanapun kehidupan mereka berubah di luar jangkaan apabila perkara pelik mula berlaku di dalam rumah. Ann segera berunding dengan bomoh yang merasakan kejahatan di dalam rumah. Dengan bantuan dari asal tuan tanah, Ann mesti membongkar rahsia ngeri sebelum kejahatan memakan seluruh keluarga.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Nang Nak
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki pulang ke rumah dari berperang di mana isteri dan anaknya menyambutnya dengan penuh semangat. Tetapi ada sesuatu yang tidak menyenangkan tentang isterinya yang cuba disampaikan oleh rakan karibnya dan orang yang baik kepadanya.

programme.title: Taxi 2
programme.desc: Duta Jepun sedang melawat Marseilles untuk melihat taktik anti-geng polis bandar. Semasa lawatan itu, bagaimanapun, dia diculik oleh kumpulan yang bekerja untuk yakuza Jepun. Pegawai muda Emilien berazam untuk menyelamatkan duta dan pegawai Petra (teman wanitanya), yang turut diculik, dan memulihkan kehormatan jabatannya. Sekali lagi, pemandu teksi syaitan laju Daniel (dari filem Teksi pertama) dipanggil untuk menyelamatkan hari dengan kemahiran memandu lajunya.

programme.title: 4 Tahun Tinggal Di Rumah Hantu
programme.desc: 4 Tahun Tinggal di Rumah Hantu adalah film horor Indonesia yang dirilis pada tahun 2014. Film ini merupakan adaptasi sebuah novel berdasarkan kisah nyata yang menceritakan rumah hantu di Kota Depok, Jawa Barat

programme.title: Zohak
programme.desc: Rustem ditangkap pada suatu petang oleh Jin yang sangat berbahaya. Selepas membunuh isterinya di hadapan anak perempuannya yang berusia enam tahun Canan, dia memenjarakan Jin dalam kotak dan membuangnya jauh ke dalam tasik. Tidak tahan dengan kesilapannya, Rustem membunuh dirinya di hadapan anak perempuannya. Canan, yang cuba melupakan apa yang dialaminya selama ini, sedang membuat persiapan untuk berkahwin dengan menjalinkan cinta yang hebat dengan Semih. Dia memberikan Canan sebuah kotak yang rakan-rakannya secara tidak sengaja ditemui di tepi tasik sebagai hadiah hari jadi, dan keadaan menjadiluarbiasa.

programme.desc: Sebuah rumah di tengah dusun tak dapat di robohkan sehingga di beli oleh faizal dan Yana. Faizal dan yana telah kehilangan anak perempuan mereka akibat kemalangan. Di dusun Yana bertemu Rinah iblis yang mendiami rumah tersebut. Rinah bagitahu Yana kalau dia boleh kembalikan anak yana yang mati. Yana lakukan ritual dan Naily benar-benar kembali. Menurut cerita rumah itu kepunyaan Rinah seorang bidan yang banyak membantu gugurkan kandungan dan suaminya Hamdi seorang bomoh. Keduanya mati di dalam rumah di bunuh penduduk kampung.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan pemenang cabutan bertuah memenangi percutian impian di resort pulau yang kelihatan indah, hanya untuk mendapati diri mereka terperangkap di pulau yang dipenuhi ular maut.

programme.desc: Dalam dunia pasca apokaliptik yang hampir akan datang, seorang bapa mesti menyeberangi landskap berbahaya untuk bersatu semula dengan isteri dan anak perempuannya.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan saintis berjaya mencipta sebuah formula bagi menggantikan minyak petrol untuk menggerakkan kereta. Walau bagaimanapun, kegembiraan mereka tidak kekal lama apabila formula tersebut telah dicuri oleh sekumpulan penjahat. Mereka cuba memburu serta mendapatkan semula formula itu daripada jatuh ke tangan orang yang tidak bertanggungjawab.

programme.title: Lurah Dendam
programme.desc: Sekumpulan ahli payung terjun yang diketuai Kapten Hanafi dalam penerbangan untuk membuat penerjunan di Kuantan. Kapal terbang yang mereka naiki terlanggar seekor burung helang dan mengakibatkan pesawat itu bergegar. Dalam keadaan kelam kabut itu, seorang demi seorang penerjun melompat keluar dan mendarat di sebuah kawasan hutan. Di sana, mereka diganggu pelbagai peristiwa dan menganggap tempat itu berpuaka. Namun, Kapten Hanafi mengesyaki semua peristiwa itu adalah berpunca daripada perbuatan manusia.

programme.title: Jaket Biru
programme.desc: Untuk menumpaskan sebuah kumpulan penyeludupan anak gadis ke luar negara, pihak polis telah menubuhkan sebuah pasukan rahsia yang bernama Jaket Biru. Pasukan yang diketuai oleh Azizan itu ditugaskan untuk melakukan intipan dengan menyertai aktiviti haram tersebut.

programme.title: Raja Laut
programme.desc: Para pelaut sering terancam dengan kegiatan seorang lanun bernama Raja Laut yang sering melakukan keganasan. Oleh kerana Raja Laut sangat licik dalam kegiatan haramnya, pihak berkuasa mengalami kesukaran untuk memberkasnya. Dalam masa yang sama, Raja Laut telah menjalinkan hubungan dengan adik seorang pegawai tentera laut yang menyukarkan lagi pihak berkuasa untuk menangkapnya.

programme.title: Gerak Khas The Movie
programme.desc: Unit Gerak Khas ditugaskan untuk menghapuskan sindiket pengedaran VCD haram dan pil khayal yang didalangi dua kumpulan. Dalam masa yang sama Inspektor Shafikah telah ditugaskan untuk membantu siasatan tersebut. Kehadiran Inspektor Shafikah disenangi oleh semua anggota unit terutamanya Inspektor Mazlan. Hal ini menimbulkan rasa cemburu Inspektor Aleza namun atas misi menghancurkan dua kumpulan penjenayah itu, dia mengenepikan soal peribadi.

programme.title: Kumpulan O
programme.desc: Sekumpulan saintis berjaya mencipta sebuah formula bagi menggantikan minyak petrol untuk menggerakkan kereta. Walau bagaimanapun, kegembiraan mereka tidak kekal lama apabila formula tersebut telah dicuri oleh sekumpulan penjahat. Mereka cuba memburu serta mendapatkan semula formula itu daripada jatuh ke tangan orang yang tidak bertanggungjawab.

programme.title: Pasung Puaka
programme.desc: Di sebuah kampung bernama Batu Rakit terdapat sebuah pasung yang digunakan untuk menghukum orang yang bersalah. Penghulu di kampung itu bernama Tok Kajai. Gadek, orang kanan Tok Kajai sering membuat onar dan cuba menggulingkannya. Pada suatu hari, seorang pemuda bernama Wira datang ke kampung itu dan sering menolong orang-orang yang teraniaya. Wira kemudiannya dilantik sebagai penolong Tok Kajai dan perkara ini telah membuatkan Gadek merasa tercabar. Gadek dan konco-konconya cuba merancang sesuatu agar Wira dapat dihukum dengan cara dipasung.

programme.title: Burung Besi
programme.desc: Azri, seorang remaja yang pintar suka bermain kapal terbang kawalan jarak jauh milik ayahnya. Dia memasang kamera pegun yang membolehkannya mengambil gambar setiap 10 saat. Gambar yang diambil olehnya telah membawanya kepada kegiatan penyeludupan milik My Lady. My Lady cuba untuk menghapuskan Azri dan rakannya supaya dia boleh kekal beroperasi.

programme.title: Ribut Di Hujung Senja
programme.desc: Andak dan seorang kawannya yang baru tiba di Pulau Segara untuk mencari akar kayu. Mereka telah diserang oleh sekumpulan samseng yang diketuai oleh Jalong sehingga mengakibatkan kematian kawannya. Penghulu telah memerintahkan supaya Andak dikurung sebelum hukuman dijatuhkan. Pada suatu malam, Antoi, anak gadis Penghulu memberi sedikit makanan kepada Andak kerana bersimpati dengan nasibnya. Apabila mendapat tahu perkara ini, Jalong berasa sakit hati kerana dia menaruh hati kepada Antoi namun tidak diendahkan. Atas nasihat anak lelakinya, Uda, Penghulu membuat satu pertandingan di antara Andak dengan Jalong untuk menentukan siapakah yang benar.

programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift
programme.desc: Dua orang sahabat, Zack dan Sham berkongsi minat yang sama iaitu perlumbaan kereta drift. Dalam masa yang sama, Zack menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fasha, seorang wanita yang turut mempunyai minat yang mendalam terhadap perlumbaan kereta drift. Walau bagaimanapun, hubungan mereka menjadi semakin dingin kerana Zack sering mengongkong hidup Fasha. Sham cuba untuk mendamaikan mereka berdua tetapi timbul pula bibit-bibit cinta antara dia dengan Fasha.

programme.title: Pecah
programme.desc: Empat orang lelaki berjaya merompak sebuah bank tetapi malangnya salah seorang daripada mereka cedera dan terpaksa dirawat di hospital. Pada masa yang sama, seorang wanita yang menjaga orang tua di sebuah rumah orang tua, membawa salah seorang penghuninya ke hospital yang sama untuk mendapatkan rawatan. Apa yang berlaku kemudiannya ialah pembongkaran demi pembongkaran agenda tersembunyi, di samping penyiasatan daripada pihak polis pada masa yang sama.

programme.title: Sumpah Semerah Padi
programme.desc: Sebuah daerah bernama Semerah Padi berada dalam keadaan aman damai di bawah pemerintahan Demang Satria. Namun, keadaan menjadi kucar kacir apabila Semerah Padi diserang oleh sekumpulan pengganas. Demang Satria mati dibunuh manakala isteri dan anak-anaknya dihalau keluar daripada Semerah Padi. Adi Putera, anak lelaki Demang Satria ialah seorang pemuda yang taat pada agama namun tidak memiliki keberanian untuk mempertahankan diri. Dia menuntut ilmu persilatan dengan Andika. programme.title: Tajwid Cinta Ep128
programme.desc: Dafri baru saja kembali ke Indonesia untuk bertemu dengan Alina dan bertunang. Walau bagaimanapun, pertunangan itu terhalang kerana Nadia tidak suka dengan hubungan Dafri Bersama anak perempuannya, Alina. Nadia dengan sengaja menghantar Dafri untuk belajar di Turki agar Dafri jauh dari anak perempuannya. Selain itu, ayah Dafri meminta Dafri untuk berkahwin dengan Syifa, seorang wanita yang pertama kali Dafri temui. Pada ketika itu, Syifa gagal berkahwin kerana bakal suaminya, Ilham, tiba-tiba menghilangkan diri. Selepas berkahwin dengan Dafri, Syifa dan suaminya tinggal di Jakarta.

programme.title: D'Academy 5 Ep37
programme.desc: D'Academy kini kembali! D'Academy atau DA (singkatan dari Dangdut Academy) ialah pertunjukan bakat muzik dangdut yang pertama dan terbesar. programme.title: Pro on their Speciality (T) Ep995
programme.desc: A popular educational documentary programs that record and reports all sorts of business stories all over the land of Taiwan

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chefs delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Defying Chase
programme.desc: A stunt man finds himself accidentally caught in an international criminal operation involving culture relics hustling and has to fight them for his life. He vows to singlehandedly take them down with his fist, and to win his dignity as well as others respect in the process.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling, a pregnant painter, moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. As she begins her one-month confinement after giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: The film follows the love story of a university student, An Ran and a Taiwanese man, Qi Xiao. They met and fell in love at a concert by Chyi Chin, a Taiwanese singer, in Beijing in 1991. However, courage alone may not be enough for the lovers to stay together, and goodbyes may truly mean the end. Will An Ran and Qi Xiao meet again in 2019?

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriends wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: High Risk
programme.desc: After failing to save his wife, Kit resigned as a cop and becomes the bodyguard and stunt double for a cowardly action film star, Frankie. When attending a jewel exhibition, they run into a band of robbers. Kit identifies the murderer of his wife amongst them and chases after him. Will Frankie regain his courage to help Kit?

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Detective Dee and Nine-storey Demon Building
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tangs demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. Dee finds the master of the family suspicious when he speaks with him, and when the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tangs strange behavior and the fact that she is kept under surveillance, Dee vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: One More Chance
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as a down-on-his-luck gambler, Water, whose ex-girlfriend asked him to take care of their autistic son. As Water lives with his son, he soon finds his goal in life. When he discovers his sons talent in running, Water decides to give up his dissipated life and support his son to achieve his dream.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: God of Gambler's Return
programme.desc: The God of Gamblers, Gao Jin, quits gambling and live a quiet life with his wife. However, a Taiwanese crime boss wants to become the new God of Gamblers and get rid of him, so he kills Gao Jins pregnant wife to force him to the casino table. Gao Jin is indignant and vows to fight the crime boss to avenge his wifes death.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the faade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: The Tag-Along: Devil Fish
programme.desc: When a man caught a fish from the lake and grilled it to eat, he heard a weird voice and saw a strange human face on the fish. Weird incidents occurred one after another, before a temple priest exorcises the malicious spirits brought on by the caught fish.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: Hail the Judge
programme.desc: A low level magistrate is run out of town for defending a beautiful murder suspect. Through a series of comedic events he ascends to the top rank & returns looking for revenge.

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kongs greatest filmmakers. It traces Huis life story and her 40-year careers ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: The Story Of Sue San
programme.desc: TIn this Huangmei Opera romance, Wang is the son of a respected government official whereas Sue San is a famous prostitute. Although they love each other and seem to be perfectly matched, the two are worlds apart when it comes to social ranking, which will prove hard to overcome...

programme.title: Swift Sword
programme.desc: A righteous swordsman, Bai Yi Pang, seeks revenge on an evil clan but is crippled after being beaten up by them. Years later, a young man encounters Bai who is hiding in a cave. Bai decides to teach this determined young man his Swift Sword skills so that he can help Bai take revenge on the evil clan.

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: Disciples Of The 36Th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: The Female Prince
programme.desc: Hsiao's stepmother frames her fianc Lung when he refuses to forfeit their engagement and sends him to prison. To save him, Hsiao disguises as Lung to take the Imperial exam and ranks first place. Impressed by Hsiao, the Emperor weds the Princess to 'him'. When Hsiao comes clean on their wedding night, she persuades the Princess to follow a plan

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: The Venus' Tear Diamond
programme.desc: Legendary rival jewel thieves Fragrant Night and Nocturnal Earl travel to Japan to steal the famous Venus Tear Diamond. They fall quickly in love at first sight, without knowing the other person is their rival and is after the same prize. Who will get the diamond, and will it mean the end of their new found love?

programme.title: Police Force
programme.desc: A man joins the Hong Kong police force to track down a murderer who has killed his friend in a robbery. While he struggles to reconcile his law defending police duty with his desire for vengeance, he also has a new-found respect for the law.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: Apartment For Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium houses owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth

programme.title: Two Con Men
programme.desc: Two Con Men is a wonderfully twisted, pseudo-romantic comedy in the vein of "Robin Hood" meets "The Sting". Starring Liang Tien as Clever Chan and Chang Ying (who's done over 400 films) as Tricky Ching, it's the age-old competition between a rookie con artist versus the ultimate, experienced flimflam man. It's a game Chen cannot afford to lose, because people's lives - including his own, hang in the balance of good versus evil.

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: The Blue And The Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: One of the great Kung-fu film characters is Beggar Su, a legendary Ching Dynasty figure who was also a member of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers. Little-known director Liu Shih-yu uses the best Kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer to tell a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure, as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liangs work, but essentially an image to him as well.

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: A professors assistant stole a micro-film storing the secret of a newly invented nuclear reactor and sells it to a crime syndicate. However, the micro-film accidentally falls into the hands of a nightclub dancer and a thief in the process, leading to them being relentlessly pursued by the crime syndicate to retrieve the micro-film.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxing
programme.desc: Chan and his apprentice Fan transport vampires for a living. In their most recent job, they are hired to transport nine zombies at one go. When two of them hopped away, it is revealed that one of them is actually a man in disguise trying to escape from his enemies. It turns out that the fake zombie and Chan are both martial arts experts!

programme.title: Rivals Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Shen and Wong Fei Hungs relationship turns sour, and Shen frames Wong and his disciple for murder. They are saved by a businessman Zhou, but Wong must win the Lion Dance Trophy to return Zhous favour. Can Wong Fei Hung defeat all skilled martial artists and complete his mission?

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: Forbidden love and magical weapons are at the centre of this enjoyable martial arts comedy. A reunited couple must recover the titular swords and avenge a murder from their past!

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponents son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chans elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: Return Of The One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: Lion Vs Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: Vanamagan
programme.desc: An Andaman tribal who escapes from men trying to capture his people, ends up in the care of a spoilt, rich girl, who starts to fall in love with him. The Film features Jayam Ravi & Sayeesha in the lead roles

Confronting their history and the frayed states of their relationships among the people who know and love them best, they ultimately reconnect in hysterical and emotionally affecting ways amid the chaos, humor, heartache and redemption that only families can provide-- driving us insane even as they remind us of our truest, and often best, selves. programme.title: Sucker Punch
programme.desc: Close your eyes. Open your mind. You will be unprepared. From the Spartan slaughter of 300 to the visionary world of Watchmen, writer/director/producer Zack Snyder has transported audiences into visual dreamscapes of his creation. His latest cinematic mind trip takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl (The Uninvited's Emily Browning) whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker institutionalized reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, but her incredible adventures blur the lines between what's real and what is imaginary. Locked away against her will, but determined to fight for her freedom, she and four other girls battle everything from serpents tosamurais on an unbelievable journey to set themselves free. Like "Alice in Wonderland with machine guns," Snyder's epic action fantasy is filmed in such a way that the action sequences aren't limited by physical real...

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep1

Pat and Jess set off to Cornwall to collect this very large special delivery in the SDS Plane whilst Ted sets about giving away all of his old inventions to the people of Greendale in order to clear out enough space for the engine. Pat and Jess meet the eccentric Ned Glenn at his workshop and wrestle with the crate containing the heavy engine to get it aboard the plane. Back in Greendale the villagers are only too delighted to take all of Ted's weird and wonderful inventions off his hands but the more inventions that go, the more gloomy Ted gets. After a trip over a very bumpy field and flight in the plane, Pat finally delivers the engine to a now very sad Ted. He's depressed because he loves to tinkering with things, and now he has nothing left to tinker with. Maybe the engine will cheer him up but when Pat takes the side off the crate, just a heap of engine parts spill out. The engine was shaken apart on the journey. Pat is very sorry but Ted is delighted. Now he has something to tinker with again! Mission accomplished!
